Guides
~~~~~~
    AmigaReport - A smaller icon than the one supplied by its creator

    AREXX       - This was actually designed for an AREXX programming
                  tool, but since it was called "AREXX Guide" I thought
                  "Hey who'll know!?"

    Game        - A default AmigaGuide icon for any game

    GrapeVine   - Designed specifically for the IRC (Internet Relay
                  Chat) program "Grapevine" (funnily enough :)

    Klondike    - A default AmigaGuide icon for "Deluxe Klondike AGA"

    MagicWB     - A replacement AmigaGuide icon for any MagicWB guides
                  created by Martin Huttenloher or anyone else

    Term        - A "general" replacement AmigaGuide icon for not only
                  "Term" but any comms program

    Tool1       - A default AmigaGuide icon for any old tool you choose

    Tool2       - An alternative to the afore mentioned AmigaGuide icon

    Utility     - Another "general" replacement AmigaGuide icon for any
                  old utility you want

    VirusChecker- An AmigaGuide icon specifically made for "VirusChecker"
                  but can be used as a "general" virus checker replacement

@ENDNODE

