    @{"OnlineMeter" LINK "Aminet"} - I like this one a lot! Mainly 'coz it was simple and
                  fast to create (and pretty too :)

 *  RCheck      - This is another replacement icon, originally from my
                  1st icon package for "ReminderCheck" which is a calendar
                  reminder type package (Sorry if this icon offends anyone!
                  see History)

 *  RecoverCED  - An update replacement icon from my original MagicWB
