History
~~~~~~~

    Version 2.0     28th Apr 1995 - Brand new icons with a few "resized"
                                    ones from version 1.0 and some default
                                    AmigaGuide icons from Roman Patzner's
                                    template (in RomIcons8).

    Version 1.0     13th Mar 1995 - First official public release includes
                                    icons, a couple of background pictures
                                    some marble-background Toolmanager
                                    dock animbrushes and a pic of my MWB.

    Version 0.9     18th Dec 1994 - Original minor release limited to only
                                    a couple of local BBS's.

@ENDNODE

